ImageCraft - BMP Image Processor
===============================

Usage:
  imagecraft <input.bmp> [output.bmp

Options:
  -h, --help           Show this help message
  -v, --version        Show version information
  -i, --info <file>    Show information about BMP file
  -g, --grayscale      Convert to grayscale
  -r, --rotate <deg>   Rotate image (90, 180, 270)
  -f, --flip <axis>    Flip image (horizontal, vertical)
  -c, --crop x y w h   Crop image

Examples:
  imagecraft input.bmp output.bmp
  imagecraft --info sample.bmp
  imagecraft -g -r 90 input.bmp rotated_gray.bmp

Supported formats:
  - 24-bit BMP without compression
  - BITMAPINFOHEADER DIB header

Project structure:
  assets/     - Input/output images
  src/        - Source code
  include/    - Header files
  aux/        - Additional resources
